Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,(Previously)\NI'm sorry, Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize that I was too focused\Non my dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.65,0:00:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,to the point that I forgot that you're\Nthe most important part of those dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.85,0:00:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be thought of as a man\Nwho never fought for your love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother\Nbeing a good husband for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.04,0:00:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard for me to change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I never forced you to marry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.51,0:00:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever tried\Nto understand my feelings? Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.47,0:02:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.81,0:02:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you shivering?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hot. Let's go to the doctor.\NInggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to the doctor now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.13,0:02:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you stand up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring your sandals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.87,0:03:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,(Emergency Unit)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,(Cipta Sehat Hospital)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you check her now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, you can't come in\Nbecause you're not wearing a mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You can buy one at the pharmacy there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- She will be handled by the nurse.\N- Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Nurse, please get the rapid test kit.\N- Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.40,0:03:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Git? Inggit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.41,0:03:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. Let's check her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tristan, do you know this patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nurse, would you bring me\Na rapid test kit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Arya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Arya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Git.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Git.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Tristan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.71,0:05:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,(Tristan)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Git.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Arya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,♪You are supposed to lecture me♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♪But then you stopped and looked at me♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I still can’t believe\NHow far you could see♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,♪All of the care that you displayed♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.22,0:06:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,♪All of the charming things\NThat you said♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.59,0:06:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Somehow made me think\NThat we are meant to be♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,♪You make me feel every love in me♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.99,0:06:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,♪You let me heal from my history♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Now you have found your way\NInto my heart to stay♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Your passion in me♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Has turned out to be♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:07:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,♪The reason\NThat I've been made complete♪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,=My Lecturer My Husband=
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.17,0:07:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts, Arya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.84,0:07:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the doctor to check this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Git.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Tristan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Nurse.\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Have you seen Tristan?\N- He's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when you're sick, you're still\Nthinking of Mr. Arya's assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.79,0:08:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Tristan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.34,0:08:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The guys in the ward\Nare looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can you take over for me, Dave?\N- I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's hands are full.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.94,0:08:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be like this, Tristan.\NThis is unprofessional.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a medical worker.\NYour responsibilities are more than...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- just your girlfriend and family.\N- Dave, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, man.\NStop being emotional like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There are nurses and doctors\Nwho will take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Doc, do you have the rapid test results?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- The result is non-reactive.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.02,0:09:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to wait\Nfor the result of the swab test.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Can she be treated at home, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's the best\Nfor the current condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.04,0:09:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have the results delivered\Nto your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The patient's gastric acid\Nwas quite bad earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For her fever, we've given the medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully her condition is better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- But she can go home.\N- She can go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes.\N- Thank you, Doc, Nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.59,0:10:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tristan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We can go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you strong enough to walk?\NOr do you want to use a wheelchair?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,(Tristan)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- Tristan.\N- Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Tristan.\N- Wait, Dave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your help in the ward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wait a minute.\N- Who are you calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm calling Inggit. Wait, Dave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Her again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- Tristan!\N- Just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh, Tristan.\NSomeone is having a heart attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The number you are calling\Nis unreachable for the moment. Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thanks.\N- You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you already have a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you want me to keep this a secret\Nfrom the whole campus, I will do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.83,0:13:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then when your boyfriend is ready,\NI will let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you want to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't tell you right now. Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I talk too much, I'm sensitive,\Nget annoyed easily, moody...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,insecure, ambitious,\Nand a perfectionist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But I love you. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'll love you even more.\N- That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I shouldn't be afraid\Nof losing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why wait for something uncertain...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,when there's something real\Nright in front of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I made breakfast for you.\NTempeh and tofu marinated in palm sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:13:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,♪All my efforts to avoid you♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,♪Are useless when I think of your smile♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.93,0:14:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,♪The further I go to leave you behind♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,♪I'm getting closer to you instead♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fever has gone down.\NHow are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Better?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring you breakfast.\NYou have to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll prepare breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Have your breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother is calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can eat by myself, Arya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- I can eat by myself.\N- Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your time. No rush.\NHere's some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hi, Arya.\N- Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. You called a few times\Nbut I didn't pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Inggit has rested.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Her fever is down, she's eating now,\Nand her condition is much better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.87,0:17:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.25,0:17:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't told her dad that she's sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid he might get worried\Nand fall ill again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,His condition\Nhas worsened a few times lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.19,0:17:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take care of Inggit.\NI will make sure everything is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:18:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This calms me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone to take care of Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you weren't there, I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, with her father's condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's okay, regarding his condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.75,0:18:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,if this could affect his health,\Nit's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we shouldn't tell him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to keep reminding Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She has to eat\Nand take her medicine on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.99,0:18:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay, Arya?\N- Yes, everything will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can count on me.\NI will take good care of Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just relax, rest,\Nand take care of her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take care of her, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is going to be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.27,0:19:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.15,0:19:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- Inggit, I don't want to argue.\N- Arya, I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.14,0:19:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to argue.\NI just want to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you care about yourself? That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Care about yourself. You're sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- I have to answer the door!\N- You are weak. Your immunity...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a medical student.\NHe must understand your condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why. He's a medical worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.22,0:19:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- Then why?\N- He won't be a danger to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He came straight from a hospital!\NHe's taking care of Covid patients!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:20:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about that!\NOh, my gosh. How do I explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Arya, at a time like this,\NI'm the one who needs to meet Tristan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who needs to see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now,\NI'm not forbidding you to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't tell me now\Nthat I'm not allowing you to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That I'm restricting you.\NI'm not trying to restrict you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- Please understand!\N- I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.34,0:20:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want you\Nto take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's it!\N- Arya. Please, I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just this time, Arya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just this time, Arya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- Arya, just this time...\N- Fine. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.58,0:20:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- Please don't be long.\N- You can't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- But you can't be here!\N- I'm going to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- I don't want to argue. Don't...\N- You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I will stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.47,0:21:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have left everything behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.76,0:21:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All of my ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All of my previous goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take care of hundreds,\Nthousands of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.24,0:22:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't take care\Nof the person I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.57,0:22:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I think of how you're alone here\Nin your condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I take care\Nof other people, Inggit?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.89,0:22:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we'll go through this together,\Nokay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.93,0:22:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Inggit?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still mad\Nabout what happened before?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.04,0:22:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So why can't I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:23:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Inggit?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.81,0:23:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how I was able to come here?\NI left my duty at the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.37,0:23:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit, you know that's my long-time\Nambition and dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.00,0:23:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that, right?\NI abandoned those things for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.21,0:23:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want, Inggit?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.01,0:23:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to go to Yogyakarta?\NDo you want me to meet your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.11,0:23:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.18,0:23:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to focus on you, Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.64,0:23:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.51,0:24:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can't come inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.08,0:25:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I love Tristan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.63,0:25:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen... Hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.75,0:27:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit, can I talk to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.75,0:27:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You were allowed to marry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.15,0:27:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't you be allowed\Nto talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.14,0:27:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thanks for letting me talk.\NNot about getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.65,0:27:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- I mean, for letting me talk because...\N- Arya.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.66,0:27:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm saying thank you not because...\N- What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.22,0:27:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.77,0:27:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to talk about...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.07,0:27:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,me, you, and Tristan.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.90,0:27:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But before I get into that,...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.28,0:27:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to explain the thinking frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.19,0:27:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So the cause and effect relationship\Nis clear. Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.69,0:28:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Arya, can you just say it simply\Nfor once?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.88,0:28:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No, listen. It's really important for me\Nto explain this structurally...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.34,0:28:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- systematically...\N- Does it really have to be structured?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.76,0:28:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it has to be because...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.71,0:28:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, ever since we're together,\Never since we're in this together...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.30,0:28:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,my life has became chaotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.45,0:28:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is it my fault?\N- No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.54,0:28:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's the thing. Not your fault.\N- You regret it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.53,0:28:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't regret it at all. I chose you.\NIt's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.73,0:28:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me first. Can I continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.31,0:28:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, what do you want to talk\Nabout me and Tristan?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.60,0:28:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,See? That's wrong.\NThis is not about you and Tristan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.58,0:28:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's about me, you, and Tristan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.71,0:28:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about you.\NIt's not about Tristan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.05,0:28:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay? I'll continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.17,0:28:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.87,0:28:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Arya. Iim is calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.89,0:29:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hi, babe.\N- Hi, babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.52,0:29:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- I miss you.\N- Yeah, miss you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.81,0:29:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Inggit,\NI want to ask you a serious question.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.03,0:29:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have to answer honestly, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.89,0:29:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? You look so serious, Iim.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.14,0:29:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're married, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.46,0:29:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Iim, how did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.80,0:29:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it on my cousin's Instagram.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.73,0:29:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the assistant\Nof a bridal makeup artist in Yogyakarta.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.11,0:29:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And she posted your pictures\Nafter getting your makeup done.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.10,0:29:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're pregnant, aren't you?\N- No, I'm not pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.81,0:29:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tristan did this to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.43,0:29:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- Not him.\N- Oh, my gosh! Then who?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.27,0:29:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not pregnant, Iim.\NI'm not pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.23,0:30:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But are you married or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.45,0:30:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't tell me you got married\Nin secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.54,0:30:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and you didn't tell your best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.01,0:30:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.99,0:30:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm mad right now. I'm going to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.90,0:30:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Iim, slow down. Slow down first.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.29,0:30:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I will tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.91,0:30:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But slow down first,\Nso I can talk to you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.72,0:30:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Iim!\N- Im!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.37,0:30:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Iim, is that Joana and Rara?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.71,0:30:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Iim. I want...\N- Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.92,0:30:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- I want some.\N- Give me some.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.56,0:30:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Just take it.\N- I want some.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.99,0:30:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- Iim, you don't want it?\N- Iim.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.89,0:30:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.17,0:30:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this mess?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.58,0:30:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Arya!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.42,0:30:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Arya! Arya!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.31,0:30:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.77,0:30:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- What is it?\N- Iim knows!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.01,0:30:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- What does she know?\N- She called.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.50,0:31:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She said I'm pregnant\Nwith Tristan's child.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.12,0:31:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you, Inggit?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.87,0:31:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm your legally wedded husband.\N- Arya, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.66,0:31:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be like this, Inggit!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.23,0:31:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- How far along is your pregnancy?\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.83,0:31:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,"What?" Enough! Just calm down.\NThe point is, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.90,0:31:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- I will take care of the baby...\N- You're not helping at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.46,0:31:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet. I'm the one who should be mad.\NNot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.71,0:31:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now listen to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.59,0:31:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Iim is calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.83,0:31:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- Iim. Im.\N- Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.96,0:31:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Iim, just wait, okay? Please. I promise\NI will explain everything to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.70,0:31:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But slow down first so...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.85,0:31:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.16,0:31:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to cry, Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.14,0:31:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How could my own best friend get married\Nbut I wasn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.92,0:31:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be your bridesmaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.62,0:31:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I already had plans for the dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.29,0:31:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's like this, everything is ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.03,0:31:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know. I'm sorry, Iim.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.62,0:32:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But please don't let Rara and Joana\Nknow about this, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.25,0:32:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you're worrying about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.86,0:32:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That they can't know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.11,0:32:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Whom are you married to? Tristan?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.02,0:32:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hi.\N- Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.45,0:32:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Iim?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.62,0:32:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Iim.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.67,0:32:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing?\NSocial distancing, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.87,0:32:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not listening\Nto the government's rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.87,0:32:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you two come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.62,0:32:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.46,0:32:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't just come here.\NSomeone invited us.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.42,0:32:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Rara invited us.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.44,0:32:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, Rara? Why don't you just\Ncall everyone and invite them here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.33,0:32:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone in our batch\Nin college so we can get Covid together?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.11,0:32:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't have the numbers\Nof everyone in our batch, Iim.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.37,0:33:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Iim is angry right now. What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.91,0:33:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is she mad?\NIs it my fault that I don't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.72,0:33:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the numbers of everyone in our batch?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.92,0:33:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the numbers either.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.83,0:33:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you\Nwe should have gone home. You...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.70,0:33:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Just relax. We are already here.\N- Come on, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.99,0:33:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat. You have food here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.42,0:33:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- You must have some food.\N- Yeah, we do, but it's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.87,0:33:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Arya, it’s become worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.37,0:33:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Arya Putra if it's a boy.\NAryani Putri if it's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.46,0:33:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- What are you talking about?\N- The name for the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.75,0:33:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's a boy,\NI want to name him Arya Putra.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.44,0:33:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Arya, what are you saying?\N- If it's a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.26,0:33:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you talking about this?\NWhat's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.26,0:33:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of what happens,\Nyour baby will be my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.33,0:33:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you crazy? We never had sex!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.20,0:33:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose fault is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.93,0:33:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Arya, I'm serious.\NWhy are you joking around?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.41,0:34:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm not joking. I'm thinking about it.\N- Thinking about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.08,0:34:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- About the name...\N- I'm not pregnant!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.50,0:34:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not pregnant with anyone's child!\NI'm not pregnant with Tristan's child!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.62,0:34:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So you and Tristan never...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.67,0:34:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.62,0:34:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of girl do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.37,0:34:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just about to say\Nthat Iim thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.01,0:34:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that I got married because I'm pregnant\Nwith Tristan's child.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.58,0:34:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I got married so fast.\NWithout letting her know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.74,0:34:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- Good.\N- "Good"?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.53,0:34:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What is so good about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.08,0:34:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I think that... Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.14,0:34:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- When she knows that you...\N- Oh, my gosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.97,0:34:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She's calling again.\NWhat should I do, Arya?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.09,0:34:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.66,0:35:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Just answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.62,0:35:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.18,0:35:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a deep breath, calm down,\Nand answer the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.67,0:35:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- Inggit.\N- Iim.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.60,0:35:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.86,0:35:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?\NWhy did you get married in secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.46,0:35:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- What happened?\N- Iim. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.82,0:35:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to tell you.\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.27,0:35:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if you're mad at me.\NI'm tired, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.34,0:35:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea\Nhow to explain this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.45,0:35:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't be sad like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.31,0:35:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing you like this makes me sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.17,0:35:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Iim, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.58,0:35:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't explain this in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.91,0:36:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But for now, don't talk about this\Nwith Joana and Rara, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.95,0:36:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Whom did you marry?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.16,0:36:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.64,0:36:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Iim, I'm so confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.98,0:36:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to make my parents happy.\NIs it wrong, Iim?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.11,0:36:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is very hard for me,\NI'm so tired of going through this, Iim.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.13,0:36:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. I can't explain anything\Nto you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.31,0:36:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.54,0:36:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.76,0:36:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.70,0:36:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.55,0:36:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.78,0:36:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.21,0:36:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Inggit.
